The Emoji Movie is an upcoming 2017 computer-animated film featuring anthropomorphic, talking Emoji characters. The movie, set for released on August 4th, is directed by Tony Leondis, animated by Sony Pictures Animation and starring T. J. Miller as Gene, Ilana Glazer as Jailbreak and Patrick Stewart as Poop.

The Emoji Movie was released on Blu-ray and DVD on October 24, 2017, by Sony Pictures Home Entertainment. Reception Box office. The Emoji Movie has grossed $86.1 million in the United States and Canada and $130.9 million in other territories, for a worldwide total of $217 million, against a production budget of $50 million.
